            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>Silv</abbr><ex>ano</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>Mag</abbr><ex>no</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>acrum</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">A</supplied>ppin</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Ser<lb break="no" n="2"/>otinus pro <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>sal</abbr><ex>ute</ex></expan> sua et su<lb break="no" n="4"/>orum <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Altar oder Basis. Zeile 1 befindet sich auf der corona. Zeile 4: VA-, ET-Ligatur. (B): CIL 03, 13460: Z. 2-3: T[--]IN Ser(gia) / [Pl]otinus. (B): CCCA; Vorbeck: Z. 1-3: [Matri] Mag(nae) s(acrum) / [---]t in Ser(gia) / [Pl]otinus.</p>
            </div>
